    "en": {
      "title": "An attack by security forces on a group of journalists in Sirasa",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four Sirasa journalists who went to report a protest in front of the Prime Minister's private residence were attacked by the security forces and four including a female journalist were admitted to the Colombo National Hospital for treatment.",
        "Sirasa Madhavedi, who was attacked, said that the attack was carried out by a group of police special forces.",
        "Media Day and others who were attacked are currently receiving treatment at the Colombo National Hospital"
      ],
